&nbsp;
“Our strong commitment to sustainable logistics is gradually becoming visible in Austria. Salzburg is now the third provincial capital, after Graz and Innsbruck, where we deliver without CO2> emissions. Every year in Salzburg we travel around 1.9 million kilometers using purely electric vehicles, saving more than 180.000 liters of diesel”, says Peter Umundum, Chief Parcel &amp; Logistics Officer at Österreichische Post AG. Austrian Posts aim to implement delivery without CO2 throughout Austria by 2030>.

